Cost-Performance-Quality Triangle Visualization. Equilateral triangle with vertices: Quality (top), Latency (bottom-left), Cost (bottom-right). Strategies as arrows inside: "Smaller Model" -> toward Cost/Latency, "Longer Prompt" -> toward Quality but away from Cost/Latency, "Caching" -> toward Cost/Latency, "Streaming" -> toward Latency (perceived), "Batching" -> toward Cost, "Speculative Decoding" -> toward Latency. German labels.